body:
### Stuff I made
* [InfaCraft](https://infacraft.net) - My other site. Lots of stuff is on there, but I never finished the front-end.
* [dSploitScripts](https://github.com/jkush321/dSploitScripts) - An Android app that allows easy downloading for scripts to inject into webpages with the dSploit Android app.
* [JBOT](https://github.com/jkush321/JBOT) - Simple RuneScape mining/treecutting/etc. bot with a nice GUI. Made in Java.
* [AutoWalls](https://github.com/jkush321/AutoWalls) - Really old but popular Minecraft "The Walls" plugin.

I'll add more projects to this page later. There are many left un-uploaded.
